{"tid":1885974,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒洩露新一代遊戲機完整規格 PS5/Xbox Series X各有勝負","createTime":"2020-02-18T15:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T17:32:57.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8080a9c67ee078b0109ab7184d5f5ef012f4d6b2","tid":1885974,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/others/76679/ps5-vs-xbox-series-x-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fothers%2F76679%2Fps5-vs-xbox-series-x-2%2F&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=2ab4fe91\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/others/76679/ps5-vs-xbox-series-x-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n作為即將上市的新一代遊戲機，PS5與Xbox Series X無疑是眾玩家關注的焦點。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報導消息，一位自稱為開發者的消息人士在論壇爆料，洩露了PS5與Xbox Series X的詳細規格，讓大家對於兩台新遊戲機的效能有了一定的了解。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指稱，其於一個擁有PS5與Xbox Series X開發者工具的協力廠商工作室擔任遊戲測試員，他們正在使用的開發者版PS5為第二版，其擁有更換硬體的功能，而SONY已經將&rdquo;調整&rdquo;過的第三版PS5交付。<br />\n<br />\n此次，其洩漏了一份開發者版PS5與Xbox Series X的詳細規格，從中可以了解到兩台新遊戲機的效能，可以說各有勝負。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">PlayStation 5：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nGPU：12.6TFLOPS（RDNA 1.5）<br />\n<br />\nCPU：AMD Zen 2 3.6GHz<br />\n<br />\n記憶體：18GB RAM,GDDR6 + 4GB DDR4<br />\n<br />\n儲存：500GB SSD，速度為5.5GB/s<br />\n<br />\n頻寬：576GB/s<br />\n<br />\n其它資訊：專門用於光線追蹤的核心及對3D音訊的支援<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">Xbox Series X：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nGPU：11.8TFLOPS（RDNA 1.5）<br />\n<br />\nCPU：AMD Zen 2 3.7GHz<br />\n<br />\n記憶體：16GB RAM,GDDR6 + 4GB DDR4<br />\n<br />\n儲存：1TB SSD，速度為3.8GB/s<br />\n<br />\n頻寬：596GB/s<br />\n<br />\n其它資訊：專門用於光線追蹤的核心<br />\n<br />\n如同之前的洩露一樣，兩台新遊戲機都將配置AMD 7nm製程的Zen 2 CPU及Navi RDNA GPU，並且此次都用上了SSD高速儲存。PS5於浮點運算及SSD速度上都稍佔優勢，但Xbox Series X擁有更高的主頻及更大的儲存容量。二者間的效能各有勝負，不過考量到上市日尚早，此應該不會是最終的版本。<br />\n<br />\n之前曾有報導指出，由於硬體成本過高，SONY對於PS5的售價左右為難。開發者版本的效能很可能與最終的零售版有所差異，或許SONY會於儲存等方面進行微調來讓售價不要虧太多。"},{"pid":"2ca36bb0657e6a2e6d6ee93c99e67f514894dd5f","tid":1885974,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:02:40.000Z","msg":"Ps5 多日系game<br />\n<br />\nXbox唔洗買game<br />\n$10 三個月pass"},{"pid":"82b747fc1ab996fa2316ad689cb4aafc385eadc4","tid":1885974,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"睇spec好勁咁 似run到4k60"},{"pid":"2a7ad12487c705073e8642861123e854d57b162e","tid":1885974,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:44:30.000Z","msg":"玩車槍球xbox又冇人<br />\n金會員又貴又過人<br />\nps又有頑皮狗獨佔鬼佬game<br />\nforza，gow同halo電腦又玩到<br />\n香港玩家九成都歸邊<br />\ngame鋪藍盒數量完全壓倒綠盒<br />\n再加香港xbox班賤種管理真係無可能唔收皮<br />\n不過Ps個on9手掣同弱智圓圈交叉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdd5f5b5c1306a1524d65a5a4f01f527443e469","tid":1885974,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"Ps5 500GB SSD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f825674000e014319c148d46c882dcc93899cbc5","tid":1885974,"uid":3764,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T01:45:43.000Z","msg":"Xbox係Gay佬先玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ef2e199f7fbdac932e7c8ae8045342af1bf36b","tid":1885974,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"第一代係咁,唔係之後點出1TB 2TB版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初發一定多伏,第一代PS4咪彈碟同熱到煎蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113af389f4d2baf34b85647c1b3006e5b976a627","tid":1885974,"uid":50124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"其實呢D 9up spec做咩成人有人轉<br />\n<br />\nD規格次次&quot;洩漏&quot;都可以完全唔同咁"},{"pid":"23fcc118ebdd2053b04bf4e1625222856a8dad88","tid":1885974,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"500GB SSD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放得幾隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}